data.description: Just move in & relax...It's ALL Done! Top to Bottom upgrades thruout this Plattsmouth Jewel. How bout this list? All new vinyl siding, new roof, the smell of fresh paint & new carpeting thruout. Match that with a new kitchen with Brand Spankin' new cabinets, SS appliances, granite counters with bonus island & porcelain tile floors with all new light fixtures. Warm & elegant wooden floors enhance the oversized living room with bay windows & 3 rooms have cool bench seat nooks. Even the trim & casings are new! 3 total brand new baths. The Primary has a brand new walk in shower with the main bath also boasting porcelain floors & Dbl sinks!  Downstairs family room is set up for the perfect theater room, with a 1/2 bath, laundry and a bonus out of site storage room. You'll also have peace of mind knowing you get a newly installed furnace, air conditioner & H2o heater for worry free living & with the vinyl windows... LOW utilities! Complete wooded lot & quiet lane offers nothing but privacy.
